01:14:10,377 --> 01:14:12,368
Figures!

988
01:14:15,377 --> 01:14:17,845
Well, hello there, Bruce Almighty.

989
01:14:20,897 --> 01:14:24,651
Not as easy as it looks, is it, son?
This God business.

990
01:14:25,617 --> 01:14:28,085
They're all out of control.

991
01:14:28,177 --> 01:14:30,247
It's me. I don't know what to do.

992
01:14:30,777 --> 01:14:33,245
Well, you're right on time.
Seven o'clock.

993
01:14:36,497 --> 01:14:38,488
The 7th at 7.00.

994
01:14:52,497 --> 01:14:54,488
All righty, then.

995
01:14:56,777 --> 01:14:59,610
- There we are.
- It's good.

996
01:15:01,817 --> 01:15:03,375
It's a wonderful thing.

997
01:15:03,457 --> 01:15:08,247
No matter how filthy something gets,
you can always clean it right up.

998
01:15:09,137 --> 01:15:12,447
There were so many.
I just gave them all what they wanted.

999
01:15:12,537 --> 01:15:14,129
Yeah.

1000
01:15:14,697 --> 01:15:18,007
But since when does anyone
have a clue about what they want?

1001
01:15:20,857 --> 01:15:23,246
So what do I do?

1002
01:15:25,777 --> 01:15:29,895
Parting your soup is not a miracle.
It's a magic trick.

1003
01:15:30,657 --> 01:15:33,125
A single mom who's working two jobs

1004
01:15:33,217 --> 01:15:37,096
and still finds time to take her kid
to soccer practice, that's a miracle.

1005
01:15:37,497 --> 01:15:40,807
A teenager who says no to drugs
and yes to an education,

1006
01:15:41,657 --> 01:15:43,648
that's a miracle.

1007
01:15:44,417 --> 01:15:46,692
People want me to do everything for them.

1008
01:15:46,777 --> 01:15:49,735
What they don't realise
is they have the power.

1009
01:15:51,017 --> 01:15:53,611
You want to see a miracle, son?

1010
01:15:53,697 --> 01:15:55,688
Be the miracle.

1011
01:15:58,897 --> 01:16:00,888
Wait. Are you leaving?

1012
01:16:01,537 --> 01:16:04,210
Yeah. I figure you can handle things now.

1013
01:16:04,297 --> 01:16:06,970
But what if I need you?
What if I have questions?

1014
01:16:07,057 --> 01:16:09,366
That's your problem, Bruce.

1015
01:16:09,457 --> 01:16:11,413
That's everybody's problem.

1016
01:16:11,497 --> 01:16:13,488
You keep looking up.

1017
01:16:17,177 --> 01:16:21,216
Orderhas been restored
after this evening's downtown riot.

1018
01:16:21,297 --> 01:16:23,970
State officials
have suspended all lottery sales

1019
01:16:24,057 --> 01:16:26,013
pending furtherinvestigation.

1020
01:16:26,097 --> 01:16:30,568
No injuries were reported in the melee,
however there were dozens ofarrests.

1021
01:17:16,617 --> 01:17:18,209
OK.

1022
01:17:19,497 --> 01:17:21,408
- Thanks a million.
- Not a problem.

1023
01:17:21,497 --> 01:17:23,488
God bless.

1024
01:17:28,017 --> 01:17:32,010
Bruce giveth and Bruce... taketh away.

1025
01:17:32,097 --> 01:17:34,657
If you don't like it... mega-bite me.

1026
01:17:42,817 --> 01:17:44,967
- Evan?
- Bruce.

1027
01:17:47,937 --> 01:17:52,806
