the anchor position. Go ahead.

1028
01:17:52,897 --> 01:17:54,888
Well, actually, I...

1029
01:17:56,097 --> 01:17:59,294
I just came to tell you
that I've been a royal prick.

1030
01:17:59,377 --> 01:18:02,096
The anchor position is yours.
I turned down the job.

1031
01:18:02,937 --> 01:18:05,246
And I never really congratulated you.

1032
01:18:06,937 --> 01:18:08,928
Congratulations.

1033
01:18:11,137 --> 01:18:12,695
Thanks, Bruce.

1034
01:18:12,777 --> 01:18:15,655
In the financial world,
things are back to normal

1035
