but they're laughing at you, pal.

1044
01:18:42,737 --> 01:18:44,853
Come on. Concentrate.

1045
01:18:44,937 --> 01:18:47,087
Pump it out, if you have to.

1046
01:18:47,177 --> 01:18:49,566
