I came for Grace's stuff.

1058
01:19:55,577 --> 01:19:58,296
- You need a...?
- That's OK. I've got it.

1059
01:20:05,177 --> 01:20:07,008
I don't know if she...

1060
01:20:07,097 --> 01:20:09,486
I don't know
if she wants that or not.

1061
01:20:13,337 --> 01:20:16,329
